name: valentina cy - for you I bought a ticket to Paris

attributes.trait_type: for you I bought a ticket to Paris

metadata.description:
I met a guy who asked me to go to Paris with him. I had only met him once, but I bought the ticket, and he booked a place for us to stay. An hour later I returned the ticket. Sometimes it's good to listen to your impulses because it makes for good art. I wrote and produced this song the next day.


I hope you like it;)
metadata.name: for you I bought a ticket to Paris  #1
metadata.title: for you I bought a ticket to Paris
